Enable legacy boot menu (f8 at startup)
 - bcdedit /set {default} bootmenupolicy legacy

Windows 10+ removed "Last Known Good Configuration" boot option

You cannot be in the Windows Insider program if you're on a local account, requires Microsoft account sign-in

Be careful with driver updater programs. Some programs (IObit Driver Booster) download bad / questionable drivers and can break components (like keyboard and mouse).
   +++ NEVER install drivers that driver updater programs find. use them as reference and look them up, then download yourself